{
  "stem": "7506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES] You know, playing with other children, non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I may have occasionally heard the name Jood, Jew in English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES] But nothing to any extent, at that time, at my age then, that-- [PAUSES] I noticed it, but it never aggravated me at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You mean amongst the Jewish friends, did we talk?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I was really-- I can't say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was fairly young in those days to discuss things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was more, you know, playful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Discussion wasn't part of my life at that age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES] We were more interested in play.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I think the time that it started to impact me more than it had done [PAUSES] was when my mother and father started to talk [PAUSES] to me and in general about Jewish people that they knew, friends or people they heard about after-- this was after Holland capitulated in the war in May 1945, [PAUSES] when it surrendered to Germany.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and father talking about Jewish people who had gone to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Had gotten out of the country in time, before all the borders were closed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is at that time that it started to impact me an awful lot that people were running away and getting out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we were left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not when I started school, but certainly after the occupation of Holland in 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I certainly remember the name Hitler, [PAUSES] because I started to hear it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My relatives, [PAUSES] all my [PAUSES] ancestors, as far as I can ascertain, and I've been able to do that through the Dutch archives in Amsterdam, from approximately 1723, [PAUSES] my ancestors all lived in Holland, both my ancestors on my mother's side and on my father's side.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
